al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5850,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/02\/anas-describes-appearance-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":11525,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Anas describes the appearance of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Rabi'ah ibn Abdur Rahman reported: I heard Anas ibn Malik describing the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cHe was of medium height among people, neither tall nor short. He had a rosy color, neither fully white nor deep brown. His hair was neither completely curly, nor quite\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/madinah-rejoice-coming-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":11525,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Madinah: People of Medina rejoice at arrival of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, arrived in Medina, the Abyssinians began playing, rejoicing at his arrival, and they played with their spears. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4923 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u062f\u0650\u0645\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/23\/entertainment-wedding-ansar\/","url_meta":{"origin":11525,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Entertainment: The Prophet entertains Ansar for a wedding","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She prepared a lady for marriage to a man among the Ansar. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Aisha, do you have any entertainment? Verily, the Ansar are fond of entertainment.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4868 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Badr al-Din al-'Ayni said, \"The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/10\/15\/prophet-loves-al-madinah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11525,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Madinah: The Prophet loves his city Medina","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, returned from a journey and saw the walls of Medina from afar, he would quicken his pace and, if he was on an animal, he would make it gallop out of his love for Medina. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":784,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/15\/ahl-al-bayt-eat-fill\/","url_meta":{"origin":11525,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet\u2019s family rarely ate to their fill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The family of Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0never ate to their fill of wheat bread for three consecutive nights, ever since they had come to Medina, until he passed away. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6089, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2970 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11525","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11525"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11525\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11525"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable"